io.proximax.sdk.model.transaction.builder

Class AliasTransactionBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.proximax.sdk.model.transaction.builder.TransactionBuilder<AliasTransactionBuilder,AliasTransaction>
      • io.proximax.sdk.model.transaction.builder.AliasTransactionBuilder

  • public class AliasTransactionBuilder
extends TransactionBuilder<AliasTransactionBuilder,AliasTransaction>

    builder for AliasTransaction

    Standard use when managing alias for mosaic: call link(MosaicId) or unlink(MosaicId)

    Standard use when managing alias for address: call link(Address) or unlink(Address)
